Packages 
Package Description
engine
Provides classes and packages of the Dare Engine.
engine.audio
Classes for playing and loading audio.
engine.audio.openal
Audio implementations using OpenAL.
engine.components
Provides various components that are useful in virtually any application.
engine.core
Classes defining the core functionality of the game engine.
engine.core.entity
Classes for defining the objects in the game and their functionality.
engine.input
Classes for reading and using input.
engine.input.opengl
Implements input classes with OpenGL compatible functions.
engine.parsing
Provides classes for loading and parsing text files.
engine.parsing.json
Provides classes for loading and parsing JSON files.
engine.rendering
Classes for rendering graphics.
engine.rendering.opengl
Classes for rendering graphics with OpenGL.
engine.space
Classes for representing and manipulating multidimensional space.
engine.util
Classes for various utility features that don't belong anywhere else.
engine.util.factory
Classes to make creating objects easier.
engine.util.menu
Classes for creating and rendering a menu.
engine.util.preprocessing
Classes designed to process data prior to usage.
